The '''warrior caste''' was the military of the [[Yinchorri/Legends|Yinchorri]], under the command of [[Yinchorri High Command]]. The Yinchorri warriors were much more aggressive and suspicious than the ruling [[Intelligentsia (Yinchorr)|Intelligentsia]].

